Package: zellij
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: A terminal workspace with batteries included
 Zellij is a workspace aimed at developers, ops-oriented people and anyone
 who loves the terminal. Similar programs are sometimes called "Terminal
 Multiplexers". Zellij is geared toward beginner and power users alike,
 allowing deep customizability, personal automation through layouts, true
 multiplayer collaboration and a plugin system allowing one to create
 plugins in any language that compiles to WebAssembly.
